channel.title: [CLIENT] Single Compile
channel.description:
A friend has asked me to host his server for him since he can't. He has provided me all the files and I said yes. Turns out that theres one edit I need to do before doing so and that is a client.java that needs to be compile in order for it to work. My computer does't seem to want to compile that for me.. Is it because of vista?
I'm asking for anyone who will do a single compile for me and that would be very appreciated.
The file is called solahclient.java for now and I will rename it once I get it back.
Thanks!
